      <title>由于国际货币基金组织暂停提供资金，肯尼亚国内借贷成本接近 2015 年以来最高水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/kenya-local-borrowing-costs-are-near-highest-since-2015-with-imf-funding-on-hold</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于融资选择的不确定性加剧，肯尼亚的本地借贷成本徘徊在近十年来的最高水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/kenya-local-borrowing-costs-are-near-highest-since-2015-with-imf-funding-on-hold</guid>
