      <title>大众汽车陷入困境之际，德国内阁批准电动汽车税收优惠政策</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/german-cabinet-approves-ev-tax-incentives-amid-volkswagen-woes</link>
